            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "text_aside",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "image_size": "medium",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "image_role": "content",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/orw-liquid-cooling-mechanics.jpg",
            "alt": "ORW Liquid cooling mechanics.jpg",
            "source_asset": "ORW Liquid cooling mechanics.jpg",
            "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
            "bytes": 264157,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 950
            }
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">將重型 IT 設備連接到裝滿的機架內的高壓液體歧管需要自動化精度，以消除人為錯誤和災難性洩漏風險。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">單擊下圖探索 Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling (PBMC) 的三個不同機械階段接合。</span></p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "divider",
          "variant": "divider",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "labeled_graphic",
          "variant": "labeledgraphic",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1",
            "media_width_variant": "medium"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "樞軸",
              "x": "14.9045163109189",
              "y": "51.73941798941799",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>在流體密封相遇之前，聯軸器接合出色的機械樞軸機構。該浮動樞軸自動使連接組件自動居中，以物理方式吸收由連接到節點底盤後部的剛性、重型液體軟管引起的任何角度偏差或結構阻力。</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "管理錯位",
              "x": "50.04712785993304",
              "y": "56.962083281663354",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>當重型服務器節點在結構罐式外殼內向前滑動時，插頭和插座流體連接器在機架框架深處相互接近。 <br><br>在此初始階段，硬件必須動態補償標準制造公差、物理框架彎曲以及服務器機箱的巨大重力。</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "流體鎖",
              "x": "89.04638381231399",
              "y": "51.42857142857142",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>在插入的最後階段，連接器乾淨地滑動在一起併發出明確的機械咔嗒聲，建立完全密封的流體路徑，能夠處理用於冷卻人工智能加速器的高流量。 <br><br>完全配合後，浮動機構將機械調節公差與主密封區域分離，確保零洩漏鎖定，無需任何手動干預。</p>"
            }
          ],
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/untitled-design-40.jpg",
