            "dimensions": {
              "width": 911,
              "height": 717,
              "originalWidth": 1280,
              "originalHeight": 720
            }
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">人工智能計算的快速發展繼續以指數速度加速。 </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">為了確保您的設施基礎設施保持高度可擴展性，工程師必須設計能夠承受下一波宏觀技術轉變的框架。</span></p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem\">單擊&nbsp;每張卡，探索即將到來的基礎設施趨勢，將Open Rack Wide架構推向其設計極限。</span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>LVDC 內向直流電和更高電壓的過渡</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">隨著功率密度需求飆升至每個外殼數百千瓦，傳統的低壓傳輸路徑遇到了嚴重的物理和效率障礙。社區正在積極探索向更高工作電壓閾值的大規模架構轉變，這將大大減少原銅電纜體積需求並減輕母線網格上嚴重的電線壓降。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>光纖和無線互連 </p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">下一代擴展網絡需要極高的數據吞吐量速度和幾乎零延遲的延遲瓶頸。未來的 ORW 迭代將無縫結合直接光學互連方案和無電纜背板配置，在相鄰服務器容器之間平穩移動大量高密度數據流，而不會阻塞結構性熱排氣通道。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "type": "flashcards",
          "variant": "flashcard",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "flashcard_size": "large"
          },
          "cards": [
            {
              "front": {
                "description_html": "<p>後勤之戰：託管與專用數據中心</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
                    "originalWidth": 1680,
                    "originalHeight": 1120
                  }
                },
                "type": "description"
              },
              "back": {
                "description_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center\">部署超重型、高密度、液冷集群在行業中造成了嚴重的物流差異。標準商業託管設施必須積極升級其強化地板限制、高架碼頭基礎設施和集中式流體設施，以匹配一級超大規模企業構建的定製、專用混凝土和冷卻環境。</p>",
                "media": {
                  "path": "resources/images/mountains.jpg",
                  "alt": "mountains.jpg",
                  "source_asset": "mountains.jpg",
                  "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                  "bytes": 160141,
                  "dimensions": {
