    {
      "id": 6,
      "slug": "knowledge-check",
      "title": "知識檢查",
      "description_html": "",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.94118\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: inherit\" data-color-scope=\"outer\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span>測試本模塊的知識。為每個問題選擇最佳答案，然後提交。</span></span></span></span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "full",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "card_mode": "WHITE",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 0,
            "padding_bottom": 0,
            "custom_padding_top": 0,
            "custom_padding_bottom": 0,
            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/black-banner-intro.png",
            "alt": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "source_asset": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 12283,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 295
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>Pivoting Blind Mate Coupling（PBMC）內部的機械樞軸機構在節點插入過程中解決什麼具體問題？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它將交流電轉換為直流電路徑。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它自動補償角度不對中和重型軟管影響，以防止連接器損壞。 </p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>當液體流速波動時，它會限制內部服務器風扇。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>它鎖定前端裝載服務器手柄以防止意外提取。</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！ PBMC 利用精確的機械樞軸來吸收結構公差變量和重型軟管阻力，確保每次都能實現安全、自對準的連接。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正確。樞軸組件的主要功能是純粹的機械對準。它動態吸收角度公差和重型軟管影響，以引導流體連接器實現完美密封。</p><p></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>哪種實現可作為高度優化的參考解決方案，旨在大規模驗證基本的 1200 毫米 ORW 框架標準？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>Open Rack V1 歷史模板</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>傳統19英寸EIA服務器機架</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>AMD Helios 參考架構</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>標準風冷 HPR 配置 </p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！ Helios 作為旗艦參考實例，展示了巨大的硅足跡和複雜的流體歧管如何在擴展的寬框架格式中完美集成。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正確。 Helios 參考架構是為證明開放式 1200 毫米 ORW 規範的水平體積和組件集成而開發的主要平臺。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>基礎設施運營商應該去哪裡找到 Open Rack Wide 框架的開源 CAD 模型、完整的工程源文件和最終的社區技術規範？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>本地硬件供應商私有目錄</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>標準商業搜索引擎圖像存儲庫</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>通用專有數據中心設施手冊</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>OCP 貢獻數據庫</p>",
              "correct": true
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！ OCP 貢獻數據庫託管對所有基本規範、工程文件和結構模型的完整、供應商中立的訪問，供全球社區使用。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正確。所有官方社區規範、接受的設計和生產就緒的 CAD 源文件都直接託管在公共、供應商中立的 OCP 貢獻數據庫中。</p>"
        },
        {
